            How to Apply These Terms to Your New Libraries

  If you develop a new library, and you want it to be of the greatest
possible use to the public, we recommend releasing it as free software
in all respects, so that the Library can be redistributed and modified
freed by anyone.  This License is therefore designed to be used to
ensure that the Library is free of charge and that source code is
made available.

